reviewText: My granddaughter loves to watch Wubbzy.
My little one watches this, and a few others all the time. She loves Wow! Wow! Wubbzy!

This DVD contains seven episodes from the Wow! Wow! Wubbzy! cartoon. Amazon doesn't always do a good job on their DVD episode listings so here are the episodes that are included on this DVD:

1. Who's That Girl
2. Welcome To The Dollhouse
3. Daizy's Hair Salon
4. Daizy's Favorite Place
5. Wonder Wubbzy
6. Daizy's Purple Thumb
7. Once Upon A Wubbzy

Each of the Wubbzy crew have their own DVD (Best of Wubbzy, Best of Widget, & Best of Walden) & finally Daizy has one too.  Voted best episodes by the online fans, this DVD contains Daizy's move to Wuzzleberg and the lessons she learns there.  She has regular adventures (like appreciating her favorite place in the park & being the new girl in town) to fun crazy ones (getting shrunk & living inside her own dollhouse).  Your kids will enjoy this compilation a lot!
